# eSim Unofficial API

A privately created API that gathers information from eSim. Currently there are only some basic tools regarding citizens and economics

## Group Citizen

### /api/{server}/citizen/{citizenID}/{id}

+ Parameters
    + server: harmonia (enum[string]) (required) 
        + Members
            + `primera`
            + `secura`
            + `suna`
            + `harmonia`
            + `terra`
            + `ww2`
    + citizenID: 123 (number) (required)

#### Get Citizen by ID [GET]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Accept: application/json

    + Body

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    Status 200

    + Body

            {
              "birthday": "cupidatat",
              "citizenship": "sint dolor dolore",
              "damage": 11977328,
              "economySkill": 5777699,
              "experience": 44524830,
              "level": -9673421,
              "location": "ut sit",
              "name": "fugiat aliqu",
              "strength": -46460406
            }

    + Schema

            {
              "type": "object",
              "required": [
                "birthday",
                "citizenship",
                "damage",
                "economySkill",
                "experience",
                "level",
                "location",
                "name",
                "strength"
              ],
              "properties": {
                "name": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "name of the citizen",
                  "example": "The Doctor"
                },
                "level": {
                  "type": "integer",
                  "description": "citizen experience level",
                  "example": 1
                },
                "experience": {
                  "type": "number",
                  "description": "number of experience points",
                  "example": 100
                },
                "damage": {
                  "type": "number",
                  "description": "total damage dealt",
                  "example": "1,000,000"
                },
                "economySkill": {
                  "type": "number",
                  "description": "total economy skill",
                  "example": 5
                },
                "strength": {
                  "type": "number",
                  "description": "number of strength points",
                  "example": "5,000"
                },
                "location": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "current location",
                  "example": "United Kingdom"
                },
                "citizenship": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "citizenship location",
                  "example": "United Kingdom"
                },
                "birthday": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "in-game day of birth",
                  "example": "Day 1"
                },
                "militaryUnit": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "name of military unit",
                  "example": "Rebel Alliance"
                },
                "party": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "name of party",
                  "example": "Monster Raving Loony Party"
                }
              }
            }

## Group Economy

